  "general_provisions": "This bill creates an education requirement to operate a watercraft.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>creates a watercraft operator safety course;<hr><ltbullet>establishes guidelines for the course;<hr><ltbullet>prohibits the operation of a watercraft without evidence of completion of the course; and<hr><ltbullet>grants rulemaking authority to the Division of Outdoor Recreation to create and manage a safety briefing for liveries.",
